fields.name: IdentityType
fields.description: Only userAssignedIdentity is supported in this API version; other types may be supported in the future

fields.name: UserAssignedIdentityResourceId
fields.description: User assigned identity to use for accessing key encryption key Url. Ex: /subscriptions/<sub uuid>/resourceGroups/<resource group>/providers/Microsoft.ManagedIdentity/userAssignedIdentities/myId.
